</p>

<p><strong>Examples:</strong> <m>1 + i = \sqrt{2} e^{i\frac{\pi}{4}}, \, 1 - i = \sqrt{2} e^{-i\frac{\pi}{4}} = \sqrt{2} e^{i\frac{7\pi}{4}}.</m></p>

